				<div class="bible-name">The Holy Bible â€“ Knox Translation</div>
				<div class="book-name">The Epistle of the Blessed Apostle Paul to the Hebrews </div>
				<div class="act-chapter">
					<div class="prev-chapter"><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20200219140047/http://catholicbible.online/knox/NT/Heb/8125">&lt; prev</a></div>|
					<div class="chapter">Chapter 10</div>
					|<div class="next-chapter"><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20200219140047/http://catholicbible.online/knox/NT/Heb/8127">next &gt;</a></div>
